SIMPLE: sidelong
RECORDS: 2

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sidelong
<hw>Side"long`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Sideling</er>, <pos>adv.</pos>]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Laterally;
obliquely; in the direction of the side.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>On the side; <as>as, to lay a thing
<ex>sidelong</ex></as>.</def> <note>[See <er>Sideling</er>,
<pos>adv.</pos> ]</note> <rj><au>Evelyn.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sidelong</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Sidelong
<hw>Side"long`</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Lateral; oblique; not being
directly in front; <as>as, a <ex>sidelong</ex> glance</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The bashful virgin's <qex>sidelong</qex> looks of love.</q>
<rj><qau>Goldsmith.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sidepiece</ent>⟦br⟧
